WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: eD3n2TN22os

NOTE Language: en

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:13.610
I bow to all the seekers of truth!

00:05:13.610 --> 00:05:31.280
At the very outset we have to know that truth
is what it is.

00:05:31.280 --> 00:05:34.220
We cannot conceptualize it.

00:05:34.220 --> 00:05:37.380
We cannot organize it.

00:05:37.380 --> 00:05:46.470
Also, we cannot know it at the stage we are,
that is, the human awareness.

00:05:46.470 --> 00:05:59.550
We have to become something subtler, something
higher, to know the truth.

00:05:59.550 --> 00:06:04.760
And to know the truth you cannot pay for it.

00:06:04.760 --> 00:06:07.970
It exists.

00:06:07.970 --> 00:06:23.340
Only our evolutionary process has brought
us to the human level and we have to know,

00:06:23.340 --> 00:06:28.540
that yet we have not known the Absolute truth.

00:06:28.540 --> 00:06:35.500
If you had known Absolute truth, there would
have been no problems, no arguments, no fighting,

00:06:35.500 --> 00:06:37.040
no wars.

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:38.930
We did not know that.

00:06:38.930 --> 00:06:48.800
And we would not know it because we have to
reach the point where we can know Absolute.

00:06:48.800 --> 00:06:56.890
So there’s a little breakthrough more needed
so that we can know the truth.

00:06:56.890 --> 00:07:07.790
When we talk of know and knowledge, we have
to understand that it’s not the mental understanding

00:07:07.790 --> 00:07:09.630
that is knowledge.

00:07:09.630 --> 00:07:20.100
For example, one of the disciples of Christ,
Thomas, travelled down to India and he wrote

00:07:20.100 --> 00:07:29.600
lots of treatise in Egypt and put them in
a big jar which was discovered about 48 years

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:30.650
back.

00:07:30.650 --> 00:07:40.480
Then they tried to decode it and a book has
already come out of it called as ‘Gnostics’.

00:07:40.480 --> 00:07:43.810
He says, those who know, are ‘Gnostics.’

00:07:43.810 --> 00:07:49.950
Now imagine the ‘Gn’ words comes from
Sanskrit meaning, to know on your central

00:07:49.950 --> 00:07:59.760
nervous system, not mental, but on your central
nervous system whatever we know is the knowledge.

00:07:59.760 --> 00:08:04.710
And those who know on their central nervous
system are the ‘Gnostics.’

00:08:04.710 --> 00:08:08.040
It’s a wonderful thing they have done.

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:14.540
But still, they are busy with the rest of
the book and they said that truth is an experience

00:08:14.540 --> 00:08:16.560
of the truth.

00:08:16.560 --> 00:08:20.090
So let us see what is the truth.

00:08:20.090 --> 00:08:29.130
Whatever I tell you today you need not accept
it blind folded but you must keep your mind

00:08:29.130 --> 00:08:36.440
open like a scientist.

00:08:36.440 --> 00:08:46.620
Whatever I say is like a hypothesis for you
and if you find it works out, then you have

00:08:46.620 --> 00:08:49.050
to accept it.

00:08:49.050 --> 00:08:53.100
As honest people, you have to accept.

00:08:53.100 --> 00:09:01.620
Now I say that the truth is that you are the
Spirit.

00:09:01.620 --> 00:09:12.870
You are not this body, mind, but you are the
Spirit and the second truth is that there

00:09:12.870 --> 00:09:25.670
is an all pervading power of God’s love
which does all the living work.

00:09:25.670 --> 00:09:27.730
We take everything for granted.

00:09:27.730 --> 00:09:37.480
For example, if we have a seed with us, we
plant it in the Mother Earth and it sprouts

00:09:37.480 --> 00:09:38.480
by itself.

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:40.950
It’s a living process.

00:09:40.950 --> 00:09:45.120
We take that living process absolutely for
granted.

00:09:45.120 --> 00:09:51.040
We don’t want to know how it works out.

00:09:51.040 --> 00:09:52.940
It’s spontaneous.

00:09:52.940 --> 00:09:55.160
Spontaneous means Sahaj.

00:09:55.160 --> 00:09:57.840
Sahaj means born with you.

00:09:57.840 --> 00:10:00.750
It is born with you.

00:10:00.750 --> 00:10:09.290
The yoga is the union with this all pervading
divine power.

00:10:09.290 --> 00:10:16.190
This state is to be achieved by all of you.

00:10:16.190 --> 00:10:25.840
Is your fundamental right, your birth right
to achieve it because if you do not achieve

00:10:25.840 --> 00:10:35.380
it, you will not know the meaning of your
life, the beauty of your being and the greatness

00:10:35.380 --> 00:10:39.050
of your existence.

00:10:39.050 --> 00:10:46.580
Like this instrument has got these wires and
if I do not put them to the mains they do

00:10:46.580 --> 00:10:47.580
not work.

00:10:47.580 --> 00:10:49.480
They have no meaning.

00:10:49.480 --> 00:10:56.330
In the same way we are to be connected to
the mains.

00:10:56.330 --> 00:11:03.180
Now about Kundalini he has already told you
about this beautiful thing that is within

00:11:03.180 --> 00:11:04.860
us.

00:11:04.860 --> 00:11:13.150
When we talk about it, you should also not
take it for granted but you can see the results

00:11:13.150 --> 00:11:17.870
that you can achieve by this kundalini awakening.

00:11:17.870 --> 00:11:26.320
Of course it’s a living process and as you
do not pay any money for sprouting a seed,

00:11:26.320 --> 00:11:31.370
in the same way you cannot pay money because
God doesn’t understand money.

00:11:31.370 --> 00:11:33.960
He doesn’t understand banking!

00:11:33.960 --> 00:11:35.900
He doesn’t understand.

00:11:35.900 --> 00:11:41.370
But somehow or the other we feel that we can
purchase God.

00:11:41.370 --> 00:11:44.410
We can pay for Him.

00:11:44.410 --> 00:11:50.300
Anybody who is available for money cannot
be your master.

00:11:50.300 --> 00:11:56.670
He cannot be a person who will deliver the
goods which are divine.

00:11:56.670 --> 00:12:04.230
So to achieve anything divine you have to
know one thing that, it is a spontaneous thing.

00:12:04.230 --> 00:12:10.620
It is the last breakthrough of your evolutionary
process and as you have not paid anything

00:12:10.620 --> 00:12:17.000
to become a human being, you don’t have
to pay anything to become a higher personality.

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:34.100
But, it’s rather surprising how we try to
think in the terms of some mundane method

00:12:34.100 --> 00:12:38.950
of achieving this higher state of awareness.

00:12:38.950 --> 00:12:49.200
It’s a living process, very simple and just
works spontaneously and the power of kundalini

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:53.820
which is shown here is your individual Mother.

00:12:53.820 --> 00:12:58.520
She is the power of pure desire.

00:12:58.520 --> 00:13:08.350
As you know, in economics it is said that
in general ‘wants are not satiable.’

00:13:08.350 --> 00:13:16.240
That means the desires, jump from one to another
but this is the pure desire which you may

00:13:16.240 --> 00:13:23.570
be aware, not aware of it but which acts and
is working within you.

00:13:23.570 --> 00:13:26.270
That’s why you’re seeking the truth.

00:13:26.270 --> 00:13:29.400
That’s why you want to know what is beyond?

00:13:29.400 --> 00:13:32.280
After all why I’m here?

00:13:32.280 --> 00:13:39.010
Everybody has this question sometime in life…why
am I on this Earth? and what am I doing here?

00:13:39.010 --> 00:13:46.810
Now the answer is only in your achieving the
state of the Spirit.

00:13:46.810 --> 00:14:00.050
The state of the Spirit is a state in which
you become a new personality with a new dimension

00:14:00.050 --> 00:14:03.430
of your awareness which Jung has described.

00:14:03.430 --> 00:14:10.210
Jung has clearly described that once when
you get your self realization you become collectively

00:14:10.210 --> 00:14:11.210
conscious.

00:14:11.210 --> 00:14:12.480
So its a question of becoming.

00:14:12.480 --> 00:14:20.540
It’s not just certifying that you are twice
born, that you are a realized soul, that you

00:14:20.540 --> 00:14:24.940
are something of a higher awareness.

00:14:24.940 --> 00:14:31.460
It is the state in which you jump.

00:14:31.460 --> 00:14:39.190
The state which you know of and you should
also know the modus operandi of the whole

00:14:39.190 --> 00:14:40.190
thing.

00:14:40.190 --> 00:14:46.700
So the yoga has two meanings; one means the
‘union’ and another meaning the ‘yukti’

00:14:46.700 --> 00:14:50.410
means the modus operandi.

00:14:50.410 --> 00:14:51.520
You must know how it works.

00:14:51.520 --> 00:14:56.020
If somebody says, alright I’ll give you
a name, I mean there have been so many from

00:14:56.020 --> 00:15:04.970
my country unfortunately, who have been selling
mantras, marketing God, marketing Ayurveda,

00:15:04.970 --> 00:15:11.130
marketing this, marketing that and people
take it for granted.

00:15:11.130 --> 00:15:12.820
They don’t know anything about it.

00:15:12.820 --> 00:15:18.210
For example TM, I was told, is so strong here,
I better not tell you how far it has gone

00:15:18.210 --> 00:15:20.170
to destroy people.

00:15:20.170 --> 00:15:28.130
But they charge, to begin with, 300 pounds
for giving mantras and they’re told you

00:15:28.130 --> 00:15:30.650
should not talk about it to anyone.

00:15:30.650 --> 00:15:36.890
Now these mantras were 3 types – one was
called as ‘inga, pinga, thinga’.

00:15:36.890 --> 00:15:41.790
These 3 words are not even Sanskrit and the
person who is supposed to be a ‘Maharishi’

00:15:41.790 --> 00:15:45.350
doesn’t even know a word of Sanskrit language!

00:15:45.350 --> 00:15:51.320
‘Inga’ means the scorpion bite, pinga
means when a person gets possessed and goes

00:15:51.320 --> 00:15:54.110
round and round, that’s ‘pinga’ and
‘thinga’ means showing like this [Shri

00:15:54.110 --> 00:15:55.110
Mataji shows Her thumb].

00:15:55.110 --> 00:15:58.490
So it was said you’re not to tell this to
anyone.

00:15:58.490 --> 00:15:59.490
It’s a secret.

00:15:59.490 --> 00:16:00.740
It’s a sacred secret!

00:16:00.740 --> 00:16:10.350
Imagine the nonsense of it and people paid
300 pounds for this so called mantra and then

00:16:10.350 --> 00:16:15.140
6000 pounds they paid, you’ll be amazed,
for becoming a ‘siddha.’

00:16:15.140 --> 00:16:19.640
Now, what is a ‘siddha’ is that they start
flying in the air!

00:16:19.640 --> 00:16:20.640
It’s nonsense!

00:16:20.640 --> 00:16:24.580
Why do you want to fly in the air about 4
feet above [you see]?

00:16:24.580 --> 00:16:28.560
Already we are having problems of the traffic.

00:16:28.560 --> 00:16:30.080
It’s absurd!

00:16:30.080 --> 00:16:32.050
How can you accept such suggestions?

00:16:32.050 --> 00:16:35.210
You’re all very intelligent people.

00:16:35.210 --> 00:16:39.060
And they said, that alright, we will give
you a siddha mantra.

00:16:39.060 --> 00:16:44.830
So they made them sit on the foam and made
them jump and then when they started jumping

00:16:44.830 --> 00:16:48.750
they broke their bottoms and there have been
cases and cases after them.

00:16:48.750 --> 00:16:56.450
6000 pounds they charge for this kind of a
nonsense and then they said that we’ll pay

00:16:56.450 --> 00:17:01.710
you, I mean you’ll have to become a very
special personality.

00:17:01.710 --> 00:17:05.710
So first they gave them the water which boils
some potatoes.

00:17:05.710 --> 00:17:07.510
It’s a fact!

00:17:07.510 --> 00:17:10.540
I’m telling the truth and I am not afraid
of them.

00:17:10.540 --> 00:17:17.520
And then they said, alright you take this
water for 6 days, 6000 pounds, imagine!

00:17:17.520 --> 00:17:26.460
And the 7th day, you take, what you call,
the rind of the potatoes and the 8th day the

00:17:26.460 --> 00:17:27.820
potatoes.

00:17:27.820 --> 00:17:28.820
For what?

00:17:28.820 --> 00:17:32.100
For going in the air just like walking up!

00:17:32.100 --> 00:17:33.100
What to say?

00:17:33.100 --> 00:17:37.870
I don’t know, it’s never described in
any one of the books.

00:17:37.870 --> 00:17:44.790
No where such a nonsense is described and
people paid.

00:17:44.790 --> 00:17:50.140
And the gentleman who was in charge of this
flying academy, became bankrupt!

00:17:50.140 --> 00:17:57.230
His wife, he, his daughter got epilepsy and
then they came to Sahaja Yoga.

00:17:57.230 --> 00:18:00.420
He is writing a book about it.

00:18:00.420 --> 00:18:05.440
I hope it comes out very soon and you will
know what these TM people are like.

00:18:05.440 --> 00:18:07.250
They are marketing everything!

00:18:07.250 --> 00:18:12.270
Now they are marketing Ayurveda.

00:18:12.270 --> 00:18:16.390
What is the need for these people to market
Ayurveda?

00:18:16.390 --> 00:18:23.710
You cannot have Ayurveda in the western countries
because its freshly prepared things.

00:18:23.710 --> 00:18:26.270
Only in India you can do it.

00:18:26.270 --> 00:18:33.810
But you can market anything to these simple
people, who have no idea as to what it is.

00:18:33.810 --> 00:18:43.420
It’s a such a shameful thing for me as an
Indian that such people should come out of

00:18:43.420 --> 00:18:47.370
my country but now I am told Americans have
taken over.

00:18:47.370 --> 00:18:52.890
Even some Australians have taken over, the
same tricks and they are minting money out

00:18:52.890 --> 00:18:56.520
of you.

00:18:56.520 --> 00:19:02.290
We had one gentleman who bought Rolls Royces
after Rolls Royces and then they were sold

00:19:02.290 --> 00:19:04.750
out, auctioned, you know him very well.

00:19:04.750 --> 00:19:07.550
What is the interest of a saint in a Rolls
Royce?

00:19:07.550 --> 00:19:08.660
I can’t understand.

00:19:08.660 --> 00:19:16.550
For example when I was in Boston they asked
me, Americans special type of brains they

00:19:16.550 --> 00:19:20.670
have, so they said, Mother, ‘how many Rolls
Royces you have?

00:19:20.670 --> 00:19:22.200
I said, ‘I have none.’

00:19:22.200 --> 00:19:23.750
‘Don’t have any Rolls Royces?’

00:19:23.750 --> 00:19:26.320
‘No, no I have my husband’s cars, that’s
all!’

00:19:26.320 --> 00:19:29.140
He said, ‘then we are not interested, it’s
no business.’

00:19:29.140 --> 00:19:32.460
I said ‘no, it’s no business at all , it’s
not a business!

00:19:32.460 --> 00:19:33.880
‘Then we are not interested.’

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:37.010
They wouldn’t even take me on the television
for that.

00:19:37.010 --> 00:19:38.300
Can you imagine!

00:19:38.300 --> 00:19:39.460
This is American brain.

00:19:39.460 --> 00:19:46.990
And that’s how they all landed in America
and they marketed everything.

00:19:46.990 --> 00:19:52.500
This is to be understood that divinity is
a pure thing.

00:19:52.500 --> 00:19:54.040
It purifies you.

00:19:54.040 --> 00:20:02.680
It has nothing to do with this materialistic
attitude of these so called saints.

00:20:02.680 --> 00:20:06.330
Saints cannot be materialistic.

00:20:06.330 --> 00:20:09.980
If they are materialistic, they are not divine.

00:20:09.980 --> 00:20:15.870
I have come here to tell you, that all these
things are within yourself.

00:20:15.870 --> 00:20:21.040
This is your own power of kundalini.

00:20:21.040 --> 00:20:24.220
She is your individual Mother.

00:20:24.220 --> 00:20:31.600
She knows each and everything about you and
She’s anxious to give you realization.

00:20:31.600 --> 00:20:44.010
And this all pervading power of God’s love,
which is described in every scripture, has

00:20:44.010 --> 00:20:52.230
come into a new mood because it was said that
there’re ‘kaliyuga,’ these horrible

00:20:52.230 --> 00:20:57.990
modern times, where all kinds of nonsensical
things will take place.

00:20:57.990 --> 00:21:08.170
And from changing it from this to ‘Satayuga,’
means the Kingdom of God, in between, in this

00:21:08.170 --> 00:21:14.320
interval, this all pervading power has gone
into another mood called as ‘kritayuga’

00:21:14.320 --> 00:21:16.420
where it is active.

00:21:16.420 --> 00:21:21.200
It is so very active that once you come to
Sahaja Yoga you’ll be surprised and you’ll

00:21:21.200 --> 00:21:22.680
say, Mother, ‘what miracles!

00:21:22.680 --> 00:21:25.030
This miracle, that miracle.’

00:21:25.030 --> 00:21:29.940
See Its God, Its GOD Almighty!

00:21:29.940 --> 00:21:34.690
For Him what is a miracle?

00:21:34.690 --> 00:21:36.550
We think of God, He’s Almighty!

00:21:36.550 --> 00:21:39.120
But we don’t know what it means.

00:21:39.120 --> 00:21:47.260
Our faith in God is so limited that we don’t
understand that He is God.

00:21:47.260 --> 00:21:51.350
My grandmother used to tell me a very sweet
story.

00:21:51.350 --> 00:21:55.700
Like the grandmother story it was…that a
man was going to see God.

00:21:55.700 --> 00:22:03.470
So one gentleman met him on the way, and asked
him, asked him, ‘if you’re going to God,

00:22:03.470 --> 00:22:08.500
then will you please tell Him that I’ve
been working very hard and when He’s going

00:22:08.500 --> 00:22:10.660
to meet me’
He said, ‘alright’

00:22:10.660 --> 00:22:15.460
Then he met one gentleman on the street, just
like on the side of the street.

00:22:15.460 --> 00:22:17.070
He said, ‘you’re going to God.

00:22:17.070 --> 00:22:21.000
Tell Him that I’ve had no food, I’ve had
no food at all’

00:22:21.000 --> 00:22:23.180
He said, ‘alright’
He was quite amazed.

00:22:23.180 --> 00:22:28.070
Look at this man just informing God that he
had no food.

00:22:28.070 --> 00:22:33.900
So he went to God and saw Him and God said
‘now, you’ve some more work?’

00:22:33.900 --> 00:22:39.040
He said, ‘no no, you see I met one gentleman
who was saying that he’s working very hard

00:22:39.040 --> 00:22:44.180
for You and when are You going to meet him
and he was making enquiries.

00:22:44.180 --> 00:22:49.380
He said that I’m waiting for Him.

00:22:49.380 --> 00:22:50.970
So You please tell me when will You meet him?’

00:22:50.970 --> 00:22:56.440
So God just smiled and said, ‘tell him to
wait for sometime, he has to wait.’

00:22:56.440 --> 00:23:02.260
Then the second one, when he told about the
second one, he said, ‘oh God that fellow

00:23:02.260 --> 00:23:05.830
was so funny, he just said that You have to
send my food.’

00:23:05.830 --> 00:23:08.930
‘Yes yes, of course his food has to be arranged
immediately.

00:23:08.930 --> 00:23:11.180
You have to do something about it.’

00:23:11.180 --> 00:23:15.490
He couldn’t understand that how these two
reactions are there.

00:23:15.490 --> 00:23:19.270
God realized that there’s something confusing
him.

00:23:19.270 --> 00:23:25.660
He told him, ‘see now you are confused.

00:23:25.660 --> 00:23:29.490
So you go down and tell one thing to both
of them and see their reactions.

00:23:29.490 --> 00:23:39.770
So just tell them that I went to God and there
I saw that He made a little camel pass through

00:23:39.770 --> 00:23:43.600
the nose of a needle.’

00:23:43.600 --> 00:23:48.480
He said, ‘really?’

00:23:48.480 --> 00:23:51.600
‘Yes, you just tell them.’

00:23:51.600 --> 00:23:53.010
He went down.

00:23:53.010 --> 00:23:56.610
The first man met him and he said, ‘what
did God, what did He say?’

00:23:56.610 --> 00:23:58.840
‘He said that you just have to wait for
a little while.

00:23:58.840 --> 00:23:59.840
I’ll come along but you have to wait.’

00:23:59.840 --> 00:24:01.600
‘So I have to still wait?’

00:24:01.600 --> 00:24:06.810
‘Yes Yes’
He said, ‘but what did you see there?’

00:24:06.810 --> 00:24:17.710
He said, ‘I saw that God, I saw a very big
miracle that He made a big elephant pass through

00:24:17.710 --> 00:24:19.710
the nose of a needle.’

00:24:19.710 --> 00:24:21.340
‘It’s not possible.

00:24:21.340 --> 00:24:22.340
How can it be?

00:24:22.340 --> 00:24:24.330
Why are you telling me stories?

00:24:24.330 --> 00:24:27.450
Because you have been to God, you’re telling
me stories?’

00:24:27.450 --> 00:24:33.770
So he went to another man and he said, ‘yes,
yes of course I knew God would give me food

00:24:33.770 --> 00:24:36.860
but I wanted to give some message so I told
you, but I’ve got it, everything.

00:24:36.860 --> 00:24:39.350
And what did you see there?

00:24:39.350 --> 00:24:49.550
So he said that, ‘that I saw that God made
a camel pass through the nose of a needle.

00:24:49.550 --> 00:24:51.420
Its a miracle!’

00:24:51.420 --> 00:24:54.670
He said, ‘what a miracle it is!

00:24:54.670 --> 00:24:56.090
It’s God.

00:24:56.090 --> 00:24:58.230
It’s God Almighty!

00:24:58.230 --> 00:25:00.520
What is it, a little camel?

00:25:00.520 --> 00:25:04.160
He can make the universes after universes
pass through that.

00:25:04.160 --> 00:25:05.710
He’s God Almighty!

00:25:05.710 --> 00:25:12.630
So you must understand that God has created
us and that we have reached the state.

00:25:12.630 --> 00:25:20.910
Now we have to just travel about 3 to 4 feet
and we are in the kingdom of God.

00:25:20.910 --> 00:25:23.810
The time has come for you to achieve it.

