It’s within yourself.

00:28:22.070 --> 00:28:26.010
It’s within yourself and it is your own
power.

00:28:26.010 --> 00:28:27.320
Its your own.

00:28:27.320 --> 00:28:28.320
So why not have it?

00:28:28.320 --> 00:28:31.490
And its freely available.

00:28:31.490 --> 00:28:38.100
Why not get to that which is your own, your
own property.

