gone head long into exploiting our Mother

00:29:33.350 --> 00:29:34.350
Earth.

00:29:34.350 --> 00:29:38.010
Any problem you take is because of human beings.

00:29:38.010 --> 00:29:46.860
So it is important to see why, we human beings
are creating problems for ourselves?

00:29:46.860 --> 00:29:58.830
And if you locate the source, it is only one
thing that we have to be transformed.

00:29:58.830 --> 00:30:06.910
The transformation of human beings is needed
and if that transformation is accepted and

00:30:06.910 --> 00:30:13.640
is worked out, if you become that beautiful
personality, then you will know what you are,

00:30:13.640 --> 00:30:22.030
how great you are, what is your potential
and what you can do.

00:30:22.030 --> 00:30:29.700
I hope today, most of you will get your realization,
I hope so and also I would like you to ask

00:30:29.700 --> 00:30:33.850
me some questions but not aggressive questions.

00:30:33.850 --> 00:30:38.740
Ask questions which are relevant because I’m
not here to take anything from you.

00:30:38.740 --> 00:30:42.640
I’m here to just give you what is yours.

