goal are material goals acceptable?

00:31:48.610 --> 00:31:55.720
If you want to do some material things, is
that acceptable?

00:31:55.720 --> 00:32:03.530
Shri Mataji: After all what is matter?

00:32:03.530 --> 00:32:06.300
Is also created by God!

00:32:06.300 --> 00:32:10.490
We can’t create anything.

00:32:10.490 --> 00:32:20.260
So, when you’re spiritually awakened you
become really extremely compassionate as well

00:32:20.260 --> 00:32:22.910
as dynamic.

00:32:22.910 --> 00:32:24.860
The energy is all the time flowing through.

00:32:24.860 --> 00:32:31.350
Now, can you believe, I am 68 years of age
and I hardly stay in a place for more than

00:32:31.350 --> 00:32:32.350
3 days.

00:32:32.350 --> 00:32:38.470
Traveling all over the world.

00:32:38.470 --> 00:32:39.470
I never get tired.

