Anything that is material as you see, for
example you want to buy something, for example.

00:32:45.490 --> 00:32:49.670
Take it, a very mundane things you see, you
want to buy.

00:32:49.670 --> 00:32:59.470
Now you want to buy something in a shop, if
it is necessary, you go in a shop and you

00:32:59.470 --> 00:33:02.170
want to know the price and everything.

00:33:02.170 --> 00:33:07.140
Now how will you know whether this is good
or bad?

00:33:07.140 --> 00:33:12.140
There’s no way to find out.

00:33:12.140 --> 00:33:17.900
But when you get self realization you start
getting these cool breeze as vibrations and

00:33:17.900 --> 00:33:24.820
your fingers become activated, finger tips
and on that you know all these centers as

00:33:24.820 --> 00:33:26.190
shown here.

