They have no conditionings of religion or
anything on their heads.

00:34:28.730 --> 00:34:30.930
Very open minded people.

00:34:30.930 --> 00:34:34.090
So, your health improves.

00:34:34.090 --> 00:34:42.630
When your health improves, your mind improves,
your intellect improves, in every way you

00:34:42.630 --> 00:34:43.980
become so relaxed.

00:34:43.980 --> 00:34:53.420
Then you see any problem, whether material
or physical, mental, emotional, any problem,

00:34:53.420 --> 00:34:55.400
as if you are out of that problem.

00:34:55.400 --> 00:34:57.350
You see that problem.

00:34:57.350 --> 00:35:00.910
And when you see that problem you can solve
it better.

00:35:00.910 --> 00:35:04.110
On any level whats so ever.

00:35:04.110 --> 00:35:06.140
Its not at all complicated.

00:35:06.140 --> 00:35:10.300
Because we are complicated, we cannot solve
the problems.

00:35:10.300 --> 00:35:16.790
I would suggest like this, if you’re standing
in the water, you’re afraid of the waves

00:35:16.790 --> 00:35:20.530
but supposing you are in a boat, you can enjoy
those waves.

00:35:20.530 --> 00:35:30.590
But supposing if you become a master of swimming
you can jump and you can save so many people.

00:35:30.590 --> 00:35:36.210
These are the stages which you pass in Sahaja
Yoga and any subject, now we have people who,

00:35:36.210 --> 00:35:40.530
say, are running factories.

