You will know why 7 times and why it is so
many times.

00:58:47.900 --> 00:58:49.460
Clockwise.

00:58:49.460 --> 00:58:51.020
Slowly.

00:58:51.020 --> 00:59:00.400
That’s all you have to do.

00:59:00.400 --> 00:59:03.520
That’s all.

