Now here you have to say or ask a question
to me.

01:00:12.850 --> 01:00:17.220
You can call me ‘Mother’ or ‘Shri Mataji,’
whatever you feel like.

01:00:17.220 --> 01:00:23.610
‘Mother, am I the Spirit?’

01:00:23.610 --> 01:00:31.230
Like a computer you’re asking a question
because you have to become a divine computer.

01:00:31.230 --> 01:00:35.730
Where the whole programming is within yourself.

01:00:35.730 --> 01:00:51.550
So now ask a question 3 times ‘Mother, am
I the Spirit?’

01:00:51.550 --> 01:00:59.500
In your heart.

01:00:59.500 --> 01:01:08.190
Now, if you are the Spirit, you are your master.

01:01:08.190 --> 01:01:17.050
So please take down your right hand in the
upper portion of your abdomen.

01:01:17.050 --> 01:01:18.440
On the left hand side.

